    # sy "You think that it's fair to only to take AmRose into your dungeon? I need a healthy amount of being dicked-down, too!"
    sy "Kau fikir adalah adil untuk hanya bawa AmRose ke penjara bawah tanah kau? Aku pun nak juga!"

# game/code/e04/e04s03.rpy:777
translate malay e04s03_end_a19e58b5:

    # mc "Well, since you're so worried about things being fair and just, you can join me as a guard."
    mc "Oleh sebab kau sangat bimbang tentang perkara yang adil dan saksama, kau boleh menyertaiaku sebagai pengawal."

# game/code/e04/e04s03.rpy:778
translate malay e04s03_end_61625a7c:

    # mc "After all, I did deputize you earlier."
    mc "Lagipun, aku memang lantik kau sebagai timbalan tadi."

# game/code/e04/e04s03.rpy:780
translate malay e04s03_end_7ddf2cbf:

    # arj "That's a great idea, Warden. Then the two of us can be here to make sure Lydia doesn't do anything stupid."
    arj "Itu idea yang bagus, Warden. Kemudian kita berdua boleh berada di sini untuk memastikan Lydia tak melakukan perkara bodoh."

# game/code/e04/e04s03.rpy:783
translate malay e04s03_end_13b09646:

    # sy "Oh she won't be doing anything stupid until she can walk straight again."
    sy "Oh dia tak akan melakukan sesuatu yang bodoh sehingga dia boleh berjalan lurus semula."

# game/code/e04/e04s03.rpy:784
translate malay e04s03_end_dcb7b57a:

    # sy "But I definitely wouldn't mind punishing her again."
    sy "Tapi aku pasti tak kesah untuk menghukumnya lagi."

# game/code/e04/e04s03.rpy:787
